OL,3,CBoy dies after being pulled from water
OL,4,Cat country park
OL,6,FA teenage boy has died after getting
OL,7,Finto difficulty in the water at a
OL,8,FSouth Yorkshire park.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FRother Valley Country Park, near
OL,12,FSheffield, at 6.50pm on Monday
OL,13,Ffollowing reports that the boy had
OL,14,Fentered the water but had failed to
OL,15,Femerge.
OL,17,FPolice, South Yorkshire Fire and
OL,18,FRescue Service and the Yorkshire
OL,19,FAmbulance Service were involved in a
OL,20,Fspecialist search operation.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
