OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779793371
OL,3,CBoy dies after being pulled from water
OL,4,Cat country park
OL,6,FA South Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Sadly, in the early hours of
OL,8,Fthis morning, a body was recovered
OL,9,Ffrom the water. Whilst formal
OL,10,Fidentification is yet to take place,
OL,11,Fthe boy's family has been informed and
OL,12,Fis being supported by officers."
OL,14,FThe boy's death was one of three
OL,15,Fsimilar incidents across the bank
OL,16,Fholiday weekend.
OL,18,FOn Sunday, 15-year-old Declan Sawyer
OL,19,Fdied at Swanholme Lakes in Lincoln.
